{"tid":1418163,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"想知要點健身先可以提升我發夢既質素","createTime":"2019-08-05T18:00:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T16:13:11.000Z","uid":163685,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"1fdba05f2edf7bbf810f501118f3f432dec66747","tid":1418163,"uid":163685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:00:50.000Z","msg":"平時無做開運動 叫偶然做下瑜珈咁<br />\n依幾個月係咁發惡夢 先發現體力好唔夠<br />\n跑又跑得慢過人 搬野又唔夠力<br />\n有簽gym 想知點樣可以有效迅速地健身健心<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nps 最好岩女仔新手簡單"},{"pid":"44e22662d26cbbb81c61699c129b1daaec19fab4","tid":1418163,"uid":204849,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:11:39.000Z","msg":"最簡單最快最有效都係練體能 跑得快好世界<br />\n走為上着"},{"pid":"cad8a8b86ec91b6a4cab81cd368768dc4d978314","tid":1418163,"uid":204849,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:12:03.000Z","msg":"試吓做HIIT嗰啲"},{"pid":"3efbb87c45ac8ba4ffa9e6c214b371983d63725a","tid":1418163,"uid":163685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cad8a8b86ec91b6a4cab81cd368768dc4d978314","tid":1418163,"uid":204849,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:12:03.000Z","msg":"試吓做HIIT嗰啲"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:17:18.000Z","msg":"係唔係求其youtube搵條片 日日做就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n洗唔洗要再去跑步重訓個啲"},{"pid":"840157738b5649c36e2345086be2a9b735f9b15b","tid":1418163,"uid":140622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:28:01.000Z","msg":"我都想知 發夢跑得唔快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a33e909453dd652c7433e5850c38f795aa0fec07","tid":1418163,"uid":48579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:28:31.000Z","msg":"跑"},{"pid":"e92a8171545375d5a21dec20ca9c56b37d4aa2ef","tid":1418163,"uid":204849,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"3efbb87c45ac8ba4ffa9e6c214b371983d63725a","tid":1418163,"uid":163685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cad8a8b86ec91b6a4cab81cd368768dc4d978314","tid":1418163,"uid":204849,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:12:03.000Z","msg":"試吓做HIIT嗰啲"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:17:18.000Z","msg":"係唔係求其youtube搵條片 日日做就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n洗唔洗要再去跑步重訓個啲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:50:27.000Z","msg":"重訓唔洗啦 唔係冇用 係要長期先有效果<br />\n跑步都要"},{"pid":"5edb42345ea92bf90a03fb48164c0e67e8cf5a67","tid":1418163,"uid":8948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:59:43.000Z","msg":"練爆發力，跑跑跑跑hiit"},{"pid":"dfa36ad75fdf6938ba32530adc60e3eec3498289","tid":1418163,"uid":107898,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:08:00.000Z","msg":"主流健身方法都要時間而未必見到成效而且需要一定知識去評估<br />\n小弟睇過本身《身體調教聖經》又譯《每週健身四小時》（The 4-hour Body) 裡面有提到一個快捷簡單既方法可以好快提升到體能，希望能幫到大家，當然呢個方法係一個入坑捷徑，希望大家多點了解運動既重要性<br />\n方法如下：<br />\n1:熱身:鑽跨(over under) 6-7下<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-YPqrauvIHg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D-YPqrauvIHg&d=bDHmYwogulq9FkNLxWxOtv7c%2B9HD3JYLAdxAiSxEDXo%3D&h=1113d999\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-YPqrauvIHg</a><br />\n2:二擇其一:<br />\na:bench press 95-85% 1rm 2-3rep + plyo push up 4-5rep 為1set, 做2-3set, 每set之間休息5分鐘<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hqhkSm0v_9o\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DhqhkSm0v_9o&d=bDHmYwogulq9FkNLxWxOtv7c%2B9HD3JYLAdxAiSxEDXo%3D&h=13217dcd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hqhkSm0v_9o</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QlsBDcMK9EY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DQlsBDcMK9EY&d=bDHmYwogulq9FkNLxWxOtv7c%2B9HD3JYLAdxAiSxEDXo%3D&h=488ab1c7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QlsBDcMK9EY</a><br />\n或<br />\nb:push up 10-12rep<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IODxDxX7oi4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DIODxDxX7oi4&d=bDHmYwogulq9FkNLxWxOtv7c%2B9HD3JYLAdxAiSxEDXo%3D&h=844a3556\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IODxDxX7oi4</a><br />\n3:deadlift: 95-85% 1rm 2-3rep(拉到膝頭就放手掉/好快放低,不必拉晒全程亦唔好慢慢落) + 原地跳 5-7rep 為1set, 做2-3set, 每set之間休息5分鐘<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XQgksUvFS1o\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DXQgksUvFS1o&d=bDHmYwogulq9FkNLxWxOtv7c%2B9HD3JYLAdxAiSxEDXo%3D&h=e1f47d22\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XQgksUvFS1o</a><br />\n4:torture twist:3-5set 3-5rep,每set之間休息30秒<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=g_16Gp01zZM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dg_16Gp01zZM&d=bDHmYwogulq9FkNLxWxOtv7c%2B9HD3JYLAdxAiSxEDXo%3D&h=5eeccc6b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=g_16Gp01zZM</a><br />\n<br />\n目的:提升肌力<br />\n方法：高重量、低次數、低訓練量，還有淡化離心收縮訓練<br />\n呢個方法仲有個好處,係可以每日練<br />\n0<br />\n0"},{"pid":"36c0864397400b1c5a3aa42611df4da875948d36","tid":1418163,"uid":85954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:08:57.000Z","msg":"Pish!"},{"pid":"661375e60bc658685b6bf082c6174697380d8dac","tid":1418163,"uid":190264,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:39:59.000Z","msg":"發前其實大部分時間都係跑，推，拉<br />\n咁所以你係訓練當中練呢三野樣就得<br />\n對於新手黎講 唔好去研究咁多動作/訓練<br />\n只會令你仲亂 又要學習個動作又成<br />\n最簡單 跑就用跑步練 <br />\n推就用掌上壓練<br />\n拉就用引體上升練<br />\n呢三樣好處係需要用多種肌肉互相配合<br />\n每次做10組掌上壓10組引體 下數根據自己能力而定 唔夠力就跪姿掌上壓/用機器減重既引體 跑步每次3-8km 隔住隔住做<br />\n一星期3日gym3日跑咁樣<br />\n一個月已經可以令你體能變到另一層次"},{"pid":"f3dac38beb7c19beb77456d60eed1bc63e9db188","tid":1418163,"uid":82359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1fdba05f2edf7bbf810f501118f3f432dec66747","tid":1418163,"uid":163685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:00:50.000Z","msg":"平時無做開運動 叫偶然做下瑜珈咁<br />\n依幾個月係咁發惡夢 先發現體力好唔夠<br />\n跑又跑得慢過人 搬野又唔夠力<br />\n有簽gym 想知點樣可以有效迅速地健身健心<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nps 最好岩女仔新手簡單"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:44:07.000Z","msg":"其實發夢都係跑，你不如直接每日都出去跑吓步"},{"pid":"7ab8a97f9e3af604d93c10a3c993c735dc53ce4e","tid":1418163,"uid":190264,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"661375e60bc658685b6bf082c6174697380d8dac","tid":1418163,"uid":190264,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:39:59.000Z","msg":"發前其實大部分時間都係跑，推，拉<br />\n咁所以你係訓練當中練呢三野樣就得<br />\n對於新手黎講 唔好去研究咁多動作/訓練<br />\n只會令你仲亂 又要學習個動作又成<br />\n最簡單 跑就用跑步練 <br />\n推就用掌上壓練<br />\n拉就用引體上升練<br />\n呢三樣好處係需要用多種肌肉互相配合<br />\n每次做10組掌上壓10組引體 下數根據自己能力而定 唔夠力就跪姿掌上壓/用機器減重既引體 跑步每次3-8km 隔住隔住做<br />\n一星期3日gym3日跑咁樣<br />\n一個月已經可以令你體能變到另一層次"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:46:37.000Z","msg":"補充多d<br />\n新手想快速好體能 <br />\n用gym room既設備訓練唔係一個好選擇 硬拉深蹲推胸 到你學識個動作 可能都發完夢了 <br />\n陣間練到又錯動作又急住加重量 <br />\n整傷左仲衰 所以做多d徒手健身會仲好<br />\n一來學習難度低好d 睇下youtube已經大概明掌上壓正確姿勢 <br />\n二來因為用自身體重 無咁易受傷"},{"pid":"2a5b87bae2d78c3b5f7244e09bf41eb0b98e33f6","tid":1418163,"uid":163685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"661375e60bc658685b6bf082c6174697380d8dac","tid":1418163,"uid":190264,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:39:59.000Z","msg":"發前其實大部分時間都係跑，推，拉<br />\n咁所以你係訓練當中練呢三野樣就得<br />\n對於新手黎講 唔好去研究咁多動作/訓練<br />\n只會令你仲亂 又要學習個動作又成<br />\n最簡單 跑就用跑步練 <br />\n推就用掌上壓練<br />\n拉就用引體上升練<br />\n呢三樣好處係需要用多種肌肉互相配合<br />\n每次做10組掌上壓10組引體 下數根據自己能力而定 唔夠力就跪姿掌上壓/用機器減重既引體 跑步每次3-8km 隔住隔住做<br />\n一星期3日gym3日跑咁樣<br />\n一個月已經可以令你體能變到另一層次"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:09:15.000Z","msg":"thx!夠簡單啱我依啲白痴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n等我聽日就開始"},{"pid":"29ccc21ac968e693176764c1752b9e42209d2407","tid":1418163,"uid":63154,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T17:05:49.000Z","msg":"練負重好耐先有成果，搬重嘢留返俾男士啦，集中練爆炸力仲好啦，跑黎講練50米段速都好夠，追求高起動速度，已經係會唔會被扑頭嘅分別<br />\n<br />\n即係咁，突然爆50米，慢慢行一段路，又突然爆50米，重複3次，如果練到最後一爆同第一爆嘅速度越來越接近，已經好撚勁"},{"pid":"4d2984e9efeb0bab61551cf1805db29236149002","tid":1418163,"uid":7306,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T14:05:53.000Z","msg":"gym撚表示<br />\n<br />\n發夢練跑步就得，重訓無乜用"},{"pid":"b0fcdc4606e320f3d46e572843cae829fdbdd93a","tid":1418163,"uid":294737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T15:19:28.000Z","msg":"留名，想增肌減脂"},{"pid":"ba2bb9c06734d15ce0677bd095182f77a2d36b96","tid":1418163,"uid":291203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T15:51:43.000Z","msg":"仲有幾樣野：<br />\n<br />\n1.反應<br />\n2.制伏技巧 （係需要d練習）<br />\n3.力量<br />\n4.肌肉 （保護骨頭，萬一被打都無咁易骨折，當然睇埋對家係咩人啦）<br />\n5.耐打能力 （萬一你中左一兩下，你都無咁應）<br />\n<br />\n利申：喺泰國食過下夜粥，日日睇住UFC班人點練"},{"pid":"2ff546558e644a72a718a93864f175b8d9d6a782","tid":1418163,"uid":85822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cad8a8b86ec91b6a4cab81cd368768dc4d978314","tid":1418163,"uid":204849,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:12:03.000Z","msg":"試吓做HIIT嗰啲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T08:21:07.000Z","msg":"堅有用 記得做住食蛋白質"},{"pid":"215f11df5630feaf005193cae328c9ca36f44e2a","tid":1418163,"uid":156331,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T01:49:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"21096c6e9a24c696ccf502960ba30d69098cce90","tid":1418163,"uid":186628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"215f11df5630feaf005193cae328c9ca36f44e2a","tid":1418163,"uid":156331,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T01:49:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T01:53:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KdJbLyF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?